  "prompt": "What are some things you should do before turning 20? Why?",
  "response": "Here are some important things to consider doing before turning 20:\n\n1. Learn financial basics\n\u2022 Create a budget\n\u2022 Start saving money\n\u2022 Understand basic investing principles\nWhy: Develops financial literacy and good money habits early\n\n2. Travel and explore\n\u2022 Visit new places\n\u2022 Experience different cultures\n\u2022 Step out of your comfort zone\nWhy: Broadens perspective, builds independence, creates memorable experiences\n\n3. Develop skills\n\u2022 Learn a foreign language\n\u2022 Take classes in something interesting\n\u2022 Pick up a practical skill (cooking, coding, etc.)\nWhy: Increases personal growth and future opportunities\n\n4. Build meaningful relationships\n\u2022 Cultivate genuine friendships\n\u2022 Learn communication skills\n\u2022 Practice emotional intelligence\nWhy: Develops social skills and support networks\n\n5. Focus on personal health\n\u2022 Establish good exercise habits\n\u2022 Learn about nutrition\n\u2022 Develop mental health awareness\nWhy: Creates foundation for long-term well-being\n\n6. Pursue personal passions\n\u2022 Try new hobbies\n\u2022 Take risks\n\u2022 Experiment with different interests\nWhy: Helps self-discovery and personal development\n\n7. Learn independence\n\u2022 Live alone/manage own expenses\n\u2022 Practice self-sufficiency\n\u2022 Make responsible decisions\nWhy: Builds crucial life skills and confidence\n\nThese experiences help create a strong foundation for personal growth and future success.",
